data.description: This beautiful move in ready home is looking for new homeowners! This 3 bed, 1 3/4 bath Bi-Level with an attached 2 car garage is located in the gated community of The Lake of the Four Seasons. Upstairs you will find the main living area illuminating natural light through the kitchen. Your culinary dreams await with updated cabinetry and plenty of countertop space all with a eat in kitchen! Down the hall you will find the master with dual closets, 2 spacious bedrooms and a updated full bath. On the lower level you will find a cozy 2nd gathering room, office, possible bedroom and updated 3/4 bath. Home has newer roof, hot water heater & has been freshly painted. Appliances are included! The backyard is perfect for entertaining with an amazing 28 ft. above ground pool, with newer liner and a pump, and is surrounded by a trex deck. All while connecting to Lions Park and the walking trail! This neighborhood offers plenty of amenities for everyone year around. You do not want to miss this!
